7 Power Banquet\nsource-banquet.html:983:                  The R&amp;R Experience\nsource-banquet.html:1030:              <a href=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards/card-selection?accent=0,0,0&accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&theme=light&venueid=10347%C2%A0\" >R&amp;R Gift Voucher</a>\nsource-banquet.html:1471:                        Lunch &amp; Dinner\nsource-banquet.html:1485:                        Lunch Specials\nsource-banquet.html:1495:                    <a href=\"/lunch-dinner#banquets\" >Banquets</a>\nsource-banquet.html:1508:                        $57 Power Banquet\nsource-banquet.html:1522:                        The R&amp;R Experience\nsource-banquet.html:1576:                    <a href=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards/card-selection?accent=0,0,0&accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&theme=light&venueid=10347%C2%A0\" >R&amp;R Gift Voucher</a>\nsource-banquet.html:1981:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h2 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>$57 POWER BANQUET</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>9-Course Lunch &amp; Early Dinner | 11am – 6pm • 7 days<br></strong>Price per person • Whole table only, min two people, max 10 people</p></div>\nsource-banquet.html:2518:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Artisan Sourdough Ciabatta - </strong><em>EVOO &amp; balsamic vinegar&nbsp;</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Jamón Ibérico - </strong><em>EVOO</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Oyster Mignonette - </strong><em>Champagne vinaigrette&nbsp;</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Wagyu Slices - </strong><em>MB 4-5 Westholme seared petit tender, R&amp;R kabayaki glaze</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Barramundi - </strong><em>Tomato coulis, Smoked miso butter, pickled shallots</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>220g MB2+ Riverina Black Angus Rump Cap - </strong><em>150+ days grain fed, Riverina, fullblood Black Angus, Glen Innes, New England Tablelands, NSW • mushroom sauce</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Charred Lettuce - </strong><em>Lemon, shaved parmesan&nbsp;</em><br><strong>Shoestring Fries </strong>- <em>Rosemary salt, aioli</em><strong><em><br></em>Dessert - </strong><em>Chef’s choice of the day</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-highlight\" data-text-attribute-id=\"eddfbdfc-3abf-45e0-9299-4fedcfcf2367\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--white\"><strong>Add ons </strong></span></span><br>Fried Egg <strong>5</strong> Foie Gras <strong>40</strong> King Prawn <strong>12</strong> Whole Live Lobster 2<strong>4</strong>0 Blue Cheese <strong>10</strong></p></div>\nsource-banquet.html:3770:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">FIND US<br>West Village Garden Pavilion<br>97 Boundary Street,<br>West End, Q 4101</p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">CAREERS<br><a href=\"/careers\">Employment</a></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br>BUSINESS OPPORTUNITIES<br><a href=\"https://www.tassisgroup.com.au/business-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\">Business Opportunities</a></p></div>\nsource-experience.html:9:<title>The Rich &amp; Rare Experience &mdash; Rich &amp; Rare Restaurant Brisbane</title>\nsource-experience.html:13:<meta prope