ience\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:1027:              <a href=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards/card-selection?accent=0,0,0&accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&theme=light&venueid=10347%C2%A0\" >R&amp;R Gift Voucher</a>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:1470:                        Lunch &amp; Dinner\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:1484:                        Lunch Specials\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:1494:                    <a href=\"/lunch-dinner#banquets\" >Banquets</a>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:1505:                        $57 Power Banquet\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:1519:                        The R&amp;R Experience\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:1573:                    <a href=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards/card-selection?accent=0,0,0&accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&theme=light&venueid=10347%C2%A0\" >R&amp;R Gift Voucher</a>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:3806:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Seafood Platter (Designed For Two) (GFO)</div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:3890:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Westholme Wagyu Tartare</div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:4058:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">MB9+ Wagyu Steak Tartare & Flintstones Bone Marrow (GF, DF)</div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:4630:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">200+ days grain-fed, 6 weeks dry aged, Black Angus / British bred, Yambinya Reserve, Northern VIC</div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:4654:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">150+ days grain-fed, Ebony Black Angus, fullblood Black Angus, raised in the Western Downs region, QLD</div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:4950:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">500+ days grain-fed, Jade Pure Wagyu, purebred Japanese wagyu, Western Downs, QLD</div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:5022:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">330+ days grain-fed, Westholme, Wagyu x Mitchell F1, Central Northern QLD</div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:5797:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h2 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\">R&amp;R SIDES</h2></div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:7056:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h4 style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Wave &amp; Wagyu - 132pp</strong></h4><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Artisan Sourdough Ciabatta<br></strong><em>Bone marrow butter</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Jamón Ibérico</strong><br><em>EVOO</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Westholme Wagyu Tartare - MB4-5 Petit Tender</strong><br><em>Yolk, fresh horseradish, homemade potato crisps</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>King Prawns</strong><br><em>Corn purée, homemade sweet chilli jam&nbsp;</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Market Fish</strong><br><em>Ask your waiter about our market fish</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Tajima Wagyu Striploin MB6-7</strong><br><em>400+ day grain fed Wagyu from Tajima bloodline cattle of Hyogo Prefecture in Japan, crossbred with Angus/Holstein, F1-F4, and raised in Australia, Riverina Region, NSW • Chimichurri</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Wagyu Fat Potatoes</strong><br><em>Gremolata, wagyu fat</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>GreenBeans</strong><br><em>Goat curd, chilli</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Chocolate</strong><br><em>Cocoa crumble, macadamia ice cream, meringue crackers, black flake salt&nbsp;</em></p></div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:7281:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h4 style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>R&amp;R EXPERIENCE - 220pp</strong></h4><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Artisan Sourdough Ciabatta<br></strong><em>Bone marrow butter</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Wagyu Tataki - MB8-9<br></strong><em>Rump, ponzu, wakame</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>King Prawns<br></strong><em>Corn purée, homemade sweet chilli jam</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Westholme Wagyu Tartare MB4-5 Petit Tender<br></strong><em>Yolk, fresh horseradish, homemade potato crisps</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Scotch Fillet<br></strong><em>150+ days grain fed, Riverina, full blood Black Angus, <br> Glen Innes, New England Tablelands, NSW</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Tajima Wagyu Striploin MB6-7<br></strong><em>300+ day grain fed Wagyu from Tajima bloodline cattle of Hyogo Prefecture in Japan, crossbred with Angus/Holstein, F1-F4, and raised in Australia, Riverina Region, NSW</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Striploin A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<br></strong><em>650+ days grain fed, 100% full blood A5 Japanese Black Wagyu, Kagoshima Japan</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>R&amp;R Red Wine Jus</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Bone Marrow Mash&nbsp;</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Green Beans&nbsp;</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Shoestring Fries&nbsp;</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Mixed Leaf Salad</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>R&amp;R Cheesecake</strong></p></div>\nsource-lunch-dinner.html:8941:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">FIND US<br>West Village Garden Pavilion<br>97 Boundary Street,<br>West End, Q 4101</p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">CAREERS<br><a href=\"/careers\">Employment</a></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br>BUSINESS OPPORTUNITIES<br><a href=\"https://www.tassisgroup.com.au/business-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\">Business Opportunities</a></p></div>\n","isError":false}

id: 81
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The live pages show the current brand is much darker and more photographic than a generic “luxury restaurant” treatment: black header, white logo, Montserrat, disciplined square-ish layout, large food/interior imagery, and a restrained warm gold accent inferred from the brand imagery and award assets. I’m codifying that now so the prototype doesn’t drift."}

