   .ds-table .num-col { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }\n202:      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n311:          <h1>Steak, seafood and a darker kind of occasion.</h1>\n330:          <h2>Four key pages, one clear booking path.</h2>\n361:          <h2>Make the menu feel premium before the PDF opens.</h2>\n404:          <h2>Dining room first, menu second, booking always close.</h2>\n418:          <h2>Private dining, vouchers and group intent stay in the main path.</h2>\n454:            <h2>Reserve at Rich &amp; Rare.</h2>\n478:        <h2>Keep the brand. Make the path sharper.</h2>\n","isError":false}

