data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The mechanical check caught one tension: the seed’s checklist wants display headings to use a serif, while the source site uses Montserrat everywhere. I’m resolving it by keeping Montserrat for logo/nav/body and using a restrained Charter/Georgia display face for the concept headlines, so the prototype reads more refined without losing the existing brand assets and structure."}

